<td align="left"><h1>Stanford University - BeHop Project</h1>
</td></tr></table>
<p><hr>
The <b>BeHop</b> research project is trying to improve the performance of WiFi networks in college dorms. 
You can learn more details <a href="details.html">here</a>. Our goal is to improve <b>your</b> WiFi performance in EV.
If you participate (it's free), we will work to make your WiFi connection faster and more reliable (better coverage, 
fewer drop outs and fewer lost connections).</p>
<p><b> BeHop is currenty available only for residents of EV Studio 5 Building. </b></p>
<p>What you need to do:</p>
<ol>
<li><p>Sign up below!</p>
</li>
<li><p>We will deliver and install your very own private WiFi AP in your room. It's small and unobtrusive (see a pic <a href="img/s5-ap.jpg">here</a> ).</p>
</li>
<li><p>That's it!! When everything is up and running, you can also enjoy a small reward :)</p>
</li>
</ol>
